<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard | Ash Tech Blogging</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #0f172a;
            --sidebar: #1e293b;
            --accent: #38bdf8;
            --text: #f8fafc;
            --card-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            display: flex;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Sidebar Navigation */
        .sidebar {
            width: 260px;
            background-color: var(--sidebar);
            border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #38bdf8, #818cf8);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .nav-links {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links li {
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        .nav-links li.active {
            background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .nav-links li:hover:not(.active) {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            color: white;
        }

        /* Main Content */
        .main-content {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 40px;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .welcome-header {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .welcome-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .welcome-header span {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        /* Acknowledgement Grid */
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .ack-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 25px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .ack-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        p {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
            color: #4ade80;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            body { flex-direction: column; }
            .sidebar { width: 100%; border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="sidebar">
        <div class="logo">Ash Tech</div>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li class="active">Overview</li>
            <li>My Articles</li>
            <li>Course Progress</li>
            <li>Settings</li>
            <a style="margin-top: auto; color: #f87171;" href="/logout">Logout</a>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <main class="main-content">
        <div class="welcome-header">
            <h1>Welcome back, <span><%=userName%></span></h1>
            <p>Here is what's happening with your tech profile today.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid">
            <div class="ack-card">
                <div class="icon">✓</div>
                <h3>Profile Verified</h3>
                <p>Your developer profile is 100% complete. You are now eligible to post articles to the community.</p>
                <div class="status-badge">Completed</div>
            </div>

            <div class="ack-card">
                <div class="icon">★</div>
                <h3>New Achievement</h3>
                <p>Congratulations! You've successfully linked your first course to your profile. Keep learning!</p>
                <div class="status-badge">New</div>
            </div>

            <div class="ack-card">
                <div class="icon">🔔</div>
                <h3>System Update</h3>
                <p>The Ash Tech 2.0 update is now live. Check out the new dark mode and faster loading speeds.</p>
                <div class="status-badge">System</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

</body>
</html>